genresAdvancedInfo.name: louange
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Louange is a genre of Christian music that originated in French-speaking countries. It is characterized by its use of traditional Christian hymns and contemporary Christian music styles such as pop, rock, and gospel. Louange music is often used in worship services and is known for its uplifting and inspirational lyrics that celebrate the love and grace of God.
